<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</h2>
<div class="developers-data-models">
<table class="govuk-table">
    <caption class="govuk-table__caption govuk-visually-hidden">Common PowerBI / COMPASS integration issues</caption>
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Symptom</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Likely cause</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Fix</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>401 UNAUTHORIZED</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Missing or malformed header.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Confirm header is <code>Authorization: Bearer cps_&hellip;</code>. Re-check token expiry at <code>/modern/admin/api-tokens</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>403 FORBIDDEN</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Token lacks scope for the endpoint.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Ask an admin to add <code>read</code> on the resource shown in the error message.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>404 NOT FOUND</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Wrong base URL or unknown id.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Verify environment (<code>compass</code> vs <code>compass-test</code>) and resource name.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Empty <code>items</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Filters too tight, or paged past <code>totalPages</code>.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Remove filters and re-run, or check <code>totalPages</code> in the envelope.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Refresh hangs in service</th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Token wired to Windows credential instead of Anonymous.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Re-edit credentials in the dataset, choose Anonymous, save.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">&ldquo;The credentials provided cannot be used for the Anonymous source&rdquo; on refresh</th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Power Query has dynamic <code>RelativePath</code> values PowerBI cannot validate.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Move all paths into <code>RelativePath</code> of a single <code>Web.Contents</code> call (as in the helper above), not into the base URL.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Schema drifted after a release</th><td class="govuk-table__cell">New nullable columns added.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Re-expand the record in Power Query; new columns are additive and never break existing reports.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
</div>

